              li Created a favorites service that alllows user to bookmark videos they want to see again
            h3(class="synopsis") Synopsis
            h4(class="synopsis") Lousy Lifehacks was inspired by <a href="http://youhole.tv/">Youhole.tv</a>, which randomly generates low view-count Youtube videos. Using EmberJS and the Youtube API, our team built this project that allows users to search a keyword or keyphrase and the site returns low view-count "How-To" videos. This site is for the amusement of those who want to watch lousy lifehackers impart their wisdom.
          
